title: Index of Factory Employment, Wearing Apparel for United States
notes:
This Index Is A Major Subindex Of The Textile Group And Combines The Following Indexes Of The Subgroup "Wearing Apparel" -- Men'S Clothing, Women'S Clothing, Corsets And Allied Garments, Men'S Furnishings, Millinery, Shirts And Collars. Source: Data For 1919-1922 Furnished To NBER Direct From Federal Reserve Board, Division Of Research And Statistics; Data For 1923-1934: Federal Reserve Bulletin, October 1938, Of Factory Employment, " October 1939, P. 8; For August 1939-1942 Data: Monthly Federal Reserve Bulletins.

This NBER data series m08091 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 8 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter08.html.

NBER Indicator: m08091
